{"tid":728317,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【黨媒】「解放軍保衛香港很偉大」","createTime":"2018-07-03T16:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T04:30:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"38fc6586eae11ced89cd246425df1b4d414375ae","tid":728317,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T16:38:57.000Z","msg":"昨日雖下大雨，卻澆不息青少年們觀看軍事演練的熱情。在看台邊，特殊一幕吸引不少記者的鏡頭，10歲姓鄧小朋友和媽媽用傘為姓楊海軍戰士擋雨，母親自己卻被大雨淋得透濕。<br />\n<br />\n打傘半小時 手軟堅持不動<br />\n<br />\n鄧同學說，該名戰士一直很有禮貌地維持秩序，下那麼大雨，卻站在雨中一動不動，他與媽媽商量要為戰士打傘，媽媽很支持，結果傘太小，只能擋住自己，媽媽卻全被淋濕了，要趕快穿上一次性雨衣擋雨。<br />\n<br />\n鄧同學足足為戰士打了逾半個小時傘，雖然手很酸軟，但也學戰士一樣一動不動，堅持到底。他說：「解放軍保衛香港，很偉大，我將來也要參軍保家衛國。」<br />\n<br />\n楊戰士入伍10個月，第一次參加軍營開放日活動，他始終嚴守軍紀筆直肅立，未有與鄧同學交談。<br />\n<br />\n當記者問他對香港市民的印象如何，他說：「香港人很熱情。」問小朋友為他打傘有何感想時，他說：「感覺心中很暖。」 <br />\n<br />\n■香港文匯報記者 殷翔<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/07/03/HK1807030018.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpaper.wenweipo.com%2F2018%2F07%2F03%2FHK1807030018.htm&d=YGuXdyIPxNHJymgc9B69yRxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=e2944137\" target=\"_blank\">http://paper.wenweipo.com/2018/07/03/HK1807030018.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f29aaa491931b0084333a4733b072ea8e2c194","tid":728317,"uid":9564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"弱智仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a548de9456f6a0610cf0b1bb99aa96ff4db9c63e","tid":728317,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T16:43:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77d9835bc4aa8668db3509c8426ea2ad973adb0","tid":728317,"uid":109459,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T17:59:12.000Z","msg":"楊彈士唔著雨褸已經弱智，鄧小朋友去幫嗰弱智士兵擔庶就更弱智，嗰阿媽嗰小個仔就仲弱智，寫呢篇文嘅人就簡直係弱智之中嘅弱智，睇同留言嘅人就更加。。。。sosad"},{"pid":"fbf003fd411ee28afaa4699b3058761d4889ce29","tid":728317,"uid":68285,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:02:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 感謝黨中央照顧了香港<br />\n感謝解放軍拯救了澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請記住 你背後有一個強大的祖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ca46575a15ab330aeafed6514e425f32996f0d1","tid":728317,"uid":93784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T18:04:13.000Z","msg":"好感動 解放軍快啲搬去大灣區啦"},{"pid":"195fe1735bc9b8bd48b1b418913aa77a3df505df","tid":728317,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08730dbf0d10451f71df04158370cabaf6e248a","tid":728317,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:01:17.000Z","msg":"唔差在跪低幫佢含埋"},{"pid":"8686900d4dd28ac923b53dadf01eb44a8c26e6f6","tid":728317,"uid":49215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:02:30.000Z","msg":"解放軍有份抗日咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f4c1b8af7be1b1becba15d5e8e45187c24e4b5","tid":728317,"uid":143499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8686900d4dd28ac923b53dadf01eb44a8c26e6f6","tid":728317,"uid":49215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:02:30.000Z","msg":"解放軍有份抗日咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T01:06:06.000Z","ms